snippet.title: TERE DIL MEIN - Rito Riba | Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair | Rajat Nagpal | Rana Sotal | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Tere Dil Mein featuring Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair.

Audio Credits :-
Singer : Rito Riba
Music Composer : Rajat nagpal
Lyrics : Rana sotal
Music composed , produced and programmed by : Rajat Nagpal 
Mixed and Mastered by : Shadab Rayeen 
Guitars : Rhythm Shaw 
Dholak & Tabla Raju : Sardar and Team 
Chorus : Sonu 
Harmonium : Paras Chopra 
Keys : Rajat Nagpal
Recorded by Rahul Sharma @ Studio 504

Video Credits :-
Production house : RS Films and Production
Director : Anishh 2.O
EP : Rahul Sahel 
Director Ad : Rajat Yadav & Aashish
Dop : Vikcee
Dop Ac : Rahul Sabharwal
Ac : Rashwinder
Choregrapher : Sumit
Production managar : Rohit Gaur, Saksham Mehta, Gulshan & Gurpreet 
Steady cam operator : sharan
Elvish and jannat makeup : Prabh makeover
Art : Karma art
Edit & DI : Inkblaze Studio
VFX : Visuals by potter
Stylist : Rajat Manchanda 
Bts : Harsh
Elvish Hair Stylist : Harry
Elvish Makeup : Parbh Makeoverz
Jannat Hair & Makeup : Ruhi Makeoverz
Junior casting : Aamir Qureshi 
Junior makeup : Sunny 

PlayDMF Team :-
Founder & CEO : Anshul Garg  
Vice President : Raghav Sharma ( Pratick Sharma)
Label Manager : Sankalp Garg
Project Head : Gaurav Arora
Legal & Digital Manager : Ashima Chauhan
PlayDMF Team : Aansi Agrawal & Anshu Prasad
Artwork : Vicky Sandhu
Accounts Manager : Sanjay Sharma & Rajkummar Jha
Asst Accounts Manager : Maninder Kaur
Special Thanks : Virgin Music India

Special Thanks : Virgin Music India
https://www.virginmusic.com/

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das, Nishtha Sikroria

Associated Brands :-
UPES Online (https://upesonline.ac.in/)
Optima Insurance Brokers Private Limited (https://optima.co.in/)

Lyrics :-
Rabb maan liya tujhko 
Jagg maan liya tujhko 
Tu he hai dunia meri 
Sabb maan liya tujhko,,

Maanga  jo paaya vahi  ,,

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Bachkay ray bachkay deewane,,
Tu naino kay khel na jaane ,,


Tu meri jaan hai yaara ,,
Tu he hai jaan say pyara ,,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara
Dhadkan banke rehna yaara ,,
Apna mujhey kehna yaara ,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara ,

Tujhey yaar kahay
Jisay pyaar kahay 
Humey toh hogea hai vahi , 

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea ,,
khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

#teredilmein #elvishyadav #elvish #jannat #jannatzubair #ritoriba

snippet.title: Daldal - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Daldal Official Trailer 
Starring Bhumi Satish Pednekkar, Aditya Rawal, Samara Tijori, Geeta Agrawal, Chinmay Mandlekar, Ananth Narayan Mahadevan, Rahul Bhat, Sandeep Kulkarni, Shivraj Walvekar, Sandesh Kulkarni, Jaya Bhattacharya, Saurabh Goyal, Vibhawari Deshpande, Emily R. Produced by Vikram Malhotra and Suresh Triveni

Created by Suresh Triveni
‚ÄúSong‚Äù ‚ÄúGumnaam Hai Koi Badnaam Hai Koi‚Äù- Under License from Saregama India Limited
¬©Ô∏è Saregama India Limited
Original Music Composer: Shankar‚ÄìJaikishan
Original Lyricist: Hasrat Jaipuri

Official Release Date - January 30, 2026 on Prime Video India

About:
RITA FERREIRA, the newly appointed DCP of the Mumbai Crime Branch, wears her crown like a curse. Introverted and plagued by impostor syndrome, Rita is shaken by the brutal murder of ‚Äì an innocent good samaritan whose death eerily mirrors a violent thought Rita had about him, just hours earlier.
Wracked with guilt, Rita is drawn to the case and, against all odds, takes it upon herself to find the killer while battling resistance from her colleagues, a deeply patriarchal system, and her unravelling personal life.
The investigation pits her against ANITA ACHARYA, a rookie reporter, whose dual existence is a scary contrast. But their true conflict isn‚Äôt with each other - it‚Äôs with the ghosts of their pasts.
What follows is a cat-and-mouse game between two women forged in trauma, set against the gritty backdrop of Mumbai and its crime branch. Only one will emerge redeemed.

snippet.description:

Today I will be playing a creepy horror game where I have to make sure that I lock everything in my house every window, every door literally everything or a haunted creepy monster/ghost will get inside.  Watch till the end to find out.
LOOK YOUR DOOR. Always lock your door before bed.
